# Only the venv management tooling and each environment's short description
# are tracked here. The actual environments are local-only: regenerable,
# machine-specific, and often huge (binaries, etc.) - not meant to live in
# git.
/*/*
!/*/comment.txt

# Marker setup.ps1 writes so vnvmgr auto-bootstraps on first use - local
# per-machine state, not something to ship.
/.setup-complete
